yName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775038399767,"sessionId":"40e095af-c088-476c-830a-bfa9dec3fdee","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":45507,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/40e095af-c088-476c-830a-bfa9dec3fdee.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个定时任务（cron job），需要我先查询 sessions_list 检测是否有活跃对话。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n2eed93yk369_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775038400212}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775038404870}}
{"type":"message","id":"d86915bc","parentId":"e46b1a1a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:13:31.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"查询结果显示只有1个session，而这个session是当前的cron任务本身（\"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\"）。这个session的消息只是当前cron任务刚发起的查询请求，不是用户活跃对话。\n\n没有其他用户活跃对话（最近5分钟内的），所以应该执行自主学习任务。\n\n接下来需要：\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n我需要使用web search技能来搜索这些信息。","thinkingSignature":"fafd2cc15226cf6aeb3ba0cc541456be98abd72ce573e716d7f0293dee12c585"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前cron任务会话，没有用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8deykn85fpit_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":817,"output":190,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44988,"cost":{"input":0.0002451,"output":0.00022799999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017925299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775038404873}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0de74b2","parentId":"d86915bc","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:13:31.048Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8deykn85fpit_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775038411044}}
